## Getting started

```bash
just bootstrap     # create the virtualenv, install deps, install git hooks
just check         # lint + format-check{% if use_mypy %} + type-check{% endif %} + tests
```

Run `just` with no arguments to list every command.

## Development

```bash
just fmt           # auto-format with ruff
just lint          # ruff lint (with --fix)
{% if use_mypy %}just type          # mypy
{% endif %}just test          # pytest{% if use_coverage %} with coverage{% endif %}
just build         # build sdist + wheel into dist/
{% if use_docs %}just docs          # serve docs locally at http://127.0.0.1:8000
{% endif %}```

